latestIgtvVideos.title: The Spice House’s Kitchen Session for The Trotter Project
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We've partnered with @thetrotterproject, an organization founded to honor the legacy of legendary chef Charlie Trotter, to participate in their Kitchen Sessions. 
In this Kitchen Session, our spice expert Alex spotlights cinnamon, peppercorns, and vanillas, and explains what makes ours so special.

Alongside chefs like @chefthomaskeller and @maneetchauhan, we're promoting The Trotter Project's COVID-19 Relief Fund, which supports underserved communities with food and contributes to the Restaurant Employee Relief Fund established by @werrestaurants and @guyfieri.

Visit our bio link to donate to The Trotter Project.

latestPosts.caption:
✨Allow us to re-introduce ourselves✨

Founded in 1957, The Spice House is a purveyor of the finest spices, herbs, signature blends, and premium extracts. We’ve spent over 60 years curating our global network of premium growers and distributors in order to offer our customers unrivaled quality and selection via our online store and our 4 shops located in Illinois and Wisconsin.

Follow along to discover the world of premium spices.

This flavor-packed Blackened Harissa Chicken is a must-try summer recipe! 🍗

This is the perfect grilled chicken dish when you want to get dinner on the table quickly with no advance prep needed. Plus, it utilizes ingredients you likely have on hand. This dish has a little heat, but the fresh orange juice and drizzle of honey not only tames the heat, but provides a sauce as well as the chicken rests. Serve with plain or herbed jasmine rice and steamed green beans. Get the full recipe at the link in our bio. ✨

Heading to the beach this week? Bring this Italian sub sandwich! 🥪🌊

At the core of our Italian Herb Blend lies an unwavering commitment to quality. Each herb is meticulously dried, and finely chopped to preserve their aromatic oils and flavors, ensuring that every pinch brings a burst of flavor. It’s perfect for elevating an array of dishes, from pastas and pizzas to meats and vegetables. 🌿

🎥: @petez.eatz

This Puff Pastry Fruit Skillet is a sweet crowd pleaser! 🍓🫐

Check dessert off your hosting list with this delicious summertime treat, elevated by our premium spices. Pick your favorite fruits for this recipe—fresh or frozen. We used blackberries, blueberries, and strawberries. Finish with a scoop of vanilla ice cream! Get the full recipe at the link in our bio. 🥧
